description: STUD FOR HIRE No.682 Cock-hungry Wes Cole turns to the 'Classifieds' to order some hot action in for the evening--and gets everything he bargained for in the person of Jeff Porter, who sports the proverbial 'Dick of Death.' After the studs have each shot a heavy load, a C-note is exchanged and baby-faced Porter is on his way to the next call.
title: The New Breed, Scene #02
